PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of BRITISH COLUMBIA of the administration and control over a number of parcels or tracts of vacant land situate near TLUPANA INLET, more particularly, Lot 128, Nootka District, and all parcels or tracts lying between it and Leagh Creek, which are to be used for a fish hatchery and other incidental purposes.
